Description: Squier by Fender Affinity Jazzmaster HH Black Electric Guitar - Return #MF43 Description This great guitar is a Christmas return because of a minor finish crack in the neck pocket, and one of the string bushings went missing and was replaced with another. Perfect for aggressive musical styles that require a pair of fat-sounding humbucking pickups, the Affinity Series Jazzmaster HH combines slick offset style with easy playability and classic Fender tone. With its comfortable “C”-shaped neck, 12”-radius rosewood fingerboard and flexible controls, the Affinity Series Jazzmaster HH is ready to rage on stage or in the studio.
